agentUtterance.text:
If you are receiving error messages, please check the following troubleshooting steps:

Payment Method (Type of payment method selected must match card being used) 

First name and Last name are spelled/entered correctly 

Address is entered correctly. Address associated with card must match the address entered 

Checking account and bank routing number were entered correctly 

Credit/Debit card number is entered correctly 

CVV/CVC is entered and correct 

Expiration month/year is correct 

If these steps don't fix your issue, please tell me the specific error code so I can provide further assistance.
